{"id":50632,"title":"Do interventions by allied health professionals discussing adherence to insulin improve this adherence?","abstract":"It is assumed that interventions to improve the adherence to insulin by allied health professionals discussing adherence to insulin will improve this adherence. However, there is little evidence to support this, as interventions by a pharmacist or nurse educator have not been shown conclusively to improve adherence to insulin. ","date":"2014-06-17","categories":"Endocrine System Diseases","split":"test","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24768512","annotations":[{"name":"Nurse","weight":0.813393,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nurse"},{"name":"Health","weight":0.765294,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Health"},{"name":"Pharmacist","weight":0.682831,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pharmacist"},{"name":"Health care provider","weight":0.669488,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Health_care_provider"},{"name":"Evidence","weight":0.172547,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Evidence"},{"name":"Insulin","weight":0.169585,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Insulin"},{"name":"Allied health professions","weight":0.139861,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Allied_health_professions"},{"name":"Teacher","weight":0.0849722,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Teacher"},{"name":"Allies","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Allies"},{"name":"Health intervention","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Health_intervention"}]}
